OL,3,C'It's barbaric': Woman with MS calls
OL,4,Cfor change to assisted dying law
OL,6,FA woman who says she has been left
OL,7,Fliving in "great discomfort" due to
OL,8,Fher multiple sclerosis (MS) is calling
OL,9,Ffor assisted suicide to be legalised
OL,10,Fin the UK.
OL,12,FAnne Jappie, 63, from Cheltenham, said
OL,13,Fshe can no longer travel to Dignitas
OL,14,Fin Switzerland unaided but doesn't
OL,15,Fwant her loved ones to be punished for
OL,16,Fhelping her.
OL,18,FShe believes she should be able to
OL,19,Fchoose when and where she wants to die
OL,20,Fand is calling for the UK law around
OL,21,Fassisting dying to be changed.
