OL,3,C'It's barbaric': Woman with MS calls
OL,4,Cfor change to assisted dying law
OL,6,FAssisted suicide and euthanasia are
OL,7,Fcurrently illegal in the UK. The law
OL,8,Fprohibits anyone from helping a person
OL,9,Fto die by suicide.
OL,11,F"It is barbaric that people are
OL,12,Fsuffering," she said. "Your pet
OL,13,Fhamster has a better chance of not
OL,14,Fbeing in pain than sentient,
OL,15,Fthoughtful, sane, people who are
OL,16,Fsuffering beyond endurance."
