OL,3,C'It's barbaric': Woman with MS calls
OL,4,Cfor change to assisted dying law
OL,6,F"If my friends were to help me, then
OL,7,Fthey would face the possibility of
OL,8,Fprosecution on return to the UK," Ms
OL,9,FJappie explained.
OL,11,FAssisted dying is already legal in
OL,12,Fcountries such as Switzerland,
OL,13,FBelgium, the Netherlands, Australia,
OL,14,FNew Zealand, Canada and several states
OL,15,F.
OL,17,FThere are growing calls for the UK to
OL,18,Fadopt a similar law, and
