OL,3,C'It's barbaric': Woman with MS calls
OL,4,Cfor change to assisted dying law
OL,6,FCritics of assisted dying argue that
OL,7,Fvulnerable people could be pressured
OL,8,Finto ending their lives prematurely if
OL,9,Fthe law is changed.
OL,11,FDr Gordon MacDonald, chief executive
OL,12,Fof the campaign group Care Not
OL,13,FKilling, said palliative should be
OL,14,Fimproved instead of legalising
OL,15,Fassisting death.
