OL,3,C'It's barbaric': Woman with MS calls
OL,4,Cfor change to assisted dying law
OL,6,F"In every jurisdiction where the law
OL,7,Fwe see the numbers go up year on year
OL,8,Fwithout any plateauing off. And we see
OL,9,Fthat the so-called safeguards get seen
OL,10,Fas barriers and are removed over
OL,11,Ftime," he said.
OL,13,F"We all feel sorry for people who are
OL,14,Fsuffering at the end of life, but
OL,15,Fproper investment in palliative care,
OL,16,Fwhich is underfunded in the UK, is the
OL,17,Fsolution to that," he added.
